race.comment: ALLERGY FREE (8) racing well without winning, placing at his last six runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on October 15 over 457m at Temora behind Irinka Fred beaten 1.5 lengths (25.92). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from four starts. Can find winning form. BIG TED (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 25.53 beating PURE SILVER. Leading chance again. PURE SILVER (6) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten half a length into second (25.56) at this track in a Grade 5 over 440m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from seven starts. Racing well and deserves a win. IRINKA ALANA (4) won last start in very good time. Sure to run well again.
